WEBVTT

00:00.011 --> 00:03.866
Test 1. For most service-based businesses,

00:03.949 --> 00:07.203
growth is often limited by manual bottleneck,

00:07.403 --> 00:10.754
time spent qualifying leads and calculating custom quotes.

00:11.775 --> 00:16.169
For this batch-cooking business, we solved that by turning a manual consultation into a

00:16.170 --> 00:20.839
digital experience. I built this custom multi-page dynamic

00:20.840 --> 00:23.314
website to serve as a high-performance,

00:23.428 --> 00:28.190
lead-capturing tool. The core is this dynamic pricing

00:28.191 --> 00:33.177
simulator. Instead of the owner manually calculating rates based on

00:33.929 --> 00:36.653
meal counts and people,

00:36.819 --> 00:41.962
the client gets an instant, accurate quote based on their specific location.

00:42.843 --> 00:48.139
When they hit submit, the lead is instantly captured.

00:48.140 --> 00:50.257
And the heavy lifting begins in the background.

00:50.296 --> 00:54.042
No manual data entry, no back and forth emails.

00:56.053 --> 01:00.810
To power these operations, I deployed a dedicated automation engine to ensure

01:00.811 --> 01:05.630
absolute privacy and compliance. The entire system is securely hosted on a cloud

01:05.631 --> 01:10.614
European server, so all client data is safe and remains strictly

01:10.615 --> 01:15.311
located within the EU. We transformed the manual administrative

01:15.312 --> 01:17.651
work into three workflows.

01:18.558 --> 01:21.062
Workflow 1, automated onboarding.

01:21.383 --> 01:24.933
Every submission is instantly synced to a master database.

01:25.317 --> 01:28.558
It doesn't just copy data, it categorizes it and formats it,

01:28.686 --> 01:32.449
ensuring the business has perfect record of every lead without lifting a finger.

01:33.932 --> 01:36.267
Workflow 2 is an intelligent booking system.

01:36.268 --> 01:39.081
This is the brain of the operation.

01:39.082 --> 01:41.941
When a session is booked with the calendar,

01:42.161 --> 01:46.854
the system performs a real-time audit, automatically checks the accounting and invoicing

01:46.855 --> 01:48.860
software to see if the customer exists,

01:49.870 --> 01:54.349
and has built custom logic to verify records by email and pull the latest

01:54.350 --> 01:58.978
pricing data, ensuring that if a client has moved or changed their plan,

01:59.113 --> 02:02.135
the billing is always available. 100% accurate.

02:03.868 --> 02:06.517
Workflow three, payment and lifecycle.

02:06.811 --> 02:11.603
Once the booking is confirmed, the system triggers the final billing stage.

02:11.982 --> 02:16.484
It cross-references the latest service history and prepares the business for

02:16.485 --> 02:20.612
payment, entirely bypassing the need for manual spreadsheets.

02:22.366 --> 02:24.395
This is a notification the owner receives.

02:24.396 --> 02:29.566
A professional formatted summary of the new booking and precise distance-based

02:29.567 --> 02:31.817
pricing and the client's contact information.

02:32.357 --> 02:34.440
This isn't just about back-end data,

02:34.650 --> 02:37.106
it's about a premium customer experience.

02:38.275 --> 02:42.021
The system is deeply integrated with the business owner's calendar,

02:42.326 --> 02:45.390
email, accounting software, and online payment system.

02:46.698 --> 02:51.366
The lead receives, firstly, an immediate automated response.

02:53.079 --> 02:58.609
It contains a personalized summary and a direct booking link synced

02:58.610 --> 03:02.966
to the owner's live availability. There's no back-and-forth on the dates.

03:03.346 --> 03:06.655
Once they book their slot, the system triggers the second phase.

03:07.323 --> 03:09.576
Here's a confirmation email the client receives.

03:10.586 --> 03:14.865
Because the system has already calculated the exact distance and price,

03:15.000 --> 03:18.767
it automatically generates and attaches the correct invoice.

03:19.989 --> 03:22.733
Simultaneously, it updates the online paying system,

03:22.932 --> 03:25.761
sending the client a secure link to finish the transaction.

03:26.333 --> 03:29.045
The owner hasn't sent a single email manually,

03:29.297 --> 03:31.903
yet the appointment is booked and the invoice is paid.

03:33.754 --> 03:38.264
I don't just build websites. I build autonomous systems that let business scales.

03:39.173 --> 03:43.840
I can take your current manual process and administration work off your

03:43.841 --> 03:46.631
hands, so you have more time to grow your business,

03:47.113 --> 03:49.505
reach more clients, and do what you do best.
